front.title: 2X-7KPR (Tooex)
front.gametext: Where present under 'nighttime conditions,' each of your Imperials and aliens at same planet site is power +2 and immune to attrition < 3.
front.lore: Basic security droid. Monitors perimeter sensors and floodlights at Imperial outposts. Responsible for maintenance of security devices. Stolen from Jabba.
